      .row
        .col-md-6
          img(src='img/sangu-tribe-logo.jpeg')
          h2 Sangu: The Tribe
          p
            | Starting from its inception, Sangu was the dominating tribe
            | on the
            a(href='http://nl.twstats.com/nl10/index.php?page=tribe&id=22147') classic NL10 server
            | .
            |           Never quite first in points but always at war with the tribe that was.
            |           Both the Sangu Package and TWTactics are tools used extensively
            |           and successfully by many Sangu players.
          p
            a.btn.btn-default(href='about', role='button') Learn more &raquo;
        .col-md-6
          img(src='img/github.png')
          h2 Contribute
          p
            | The source code for both
            a(href='https://github.com/SanguPackage/Script') Sangu Package
            |             and
            a(href='https://github.com/SanguPackage/TWTactics') TW Tactics
            |  is available
            |             on
            a(href='https://github.com/SanguPackage') GitHub
            | .
          p
            | If you are new to JavaScript, some guidelines and information about how to start building a script
            | for Tribal Wars can be found
            a(href='http://forum.tribalwars.nl/showthread.php?117006-Hoe-ontwikkel-je-een-TW-script') on the forum (Dutch)
            | .
          p
            a.btn.btn-default(href='support', role='button') Learn more &raquo;
      hr
